      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material certificates provided by DePuy Synthes for each manufacturing lot. CMM dimensional inspection performed on three representative screws per lot. Nominal CAD geometry used for FEA with as-measured dimensional deviations < 0.05 mm, within model sensitivity threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
