      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria. E/uval values: 1.41 (stiffness), 1.18 (yield force), 0.97 (force at 40 mm). Percent differences: 4.2%, 6.8%, 5.1%. Validation metric framework follows ASME V&V 10.1-2012."
